>
  <h1>Simmer</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Kitchen timers that live in your Dynamic Island. Every pot, one glance.</p>

  <ul class="features">
    <li><strong>Run every burner at once</strong>
        <span>Pasta, sauce, and the oven each get their own timer, laid out like your stove.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Glance, don't unlock</strong>
        <span>All timers stay live in your Dynamic Island and on your Lock Screen until they're done.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Private by design</strong>
        <span>No account, no ads, no tracking. Simmer works entirely on your device.</span></li>
  </ul>

  <span class="badge">Coming soon to the App Store</span>

